data.title: Combat Communications Exercise in Texas Prepares Airmen
data.meta_description: Communications non-commissioned officers Tech Sgt. Darrell Harris, 644 Combat Communications Squadron, Andersen Air Force Base Guam and Staff Sgt. Timothy Hoover, 221st Combat Communications Squadron, Garland Air National Guard Station, Texas practice their satellite communications skills during the advanced theater deployable communications exercise at Garland Air National Guard Station, Texas on May 4.
